Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.68,0:00:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[新機動戰記-鋼彈W]\NJust Wild Beat Communication
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.61,0:00:19.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.08,0:00:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決不褪色的熾熱思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.62,0:00:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳遍你的全身 TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.73,0:00:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱著你被淋濕的肩膀 想溫暖你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.94,0:00:48.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,顫抖的指尖 彷徨地在找什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.74,0:00:54.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想留住你的視線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.02,0:01:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信把悲傷變為力量的愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.46,0:01:10.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.13,0:01:13.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決不褪色的熾熱思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.77,0:01:17.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳遍你的全身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.47,0:01:19.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.08,0:01:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,離開地球的人類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.32,0:01:26.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在宇宙殖民衛星的生活裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.15,0:01:28.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尋找新的希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.02,0:01:31.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，地球圈統一聯合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.89,0:01:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,藉正義及和平為名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.96,0:01:36.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以壓倒性的軍事力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.33,0:01:38.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,壓制著各個殖民衛星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.37,0:01:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ac195年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.83,0:01:46.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作戰名稱[流星作戰]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.20,0:01:50.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和聯合反目的部份衛星居民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.08,0:01:52.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決定把偽裝為流星的新武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.48,0:01:55.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,送落地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.35,0:01:57.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，這次作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.12,0:02:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早已被聯合總部發覺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.52,0:02:05.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們不可以戰鬥!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.10,0:02:16.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請別這樣，因為是我先走出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.57,0:02:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第四話\N[惡夢的維多利亞]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.08,0:02:35.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,柯西嘉工場有情報進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.32,0:02:37.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,援軍來到時敵人已經消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.79,0:02:40.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,損毀程度好像有55%
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.49,0:02:43.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,華卡，兩部新敵機的資料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.63,0:02:45.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.66,0:02:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑克斯上級特尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.13,0:02:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和維多利亞基地聯絡上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.04,0:02:56.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很久不見呢，傑克斯特尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.04,0:02:58.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你仍然沒變，諾茵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.04,0:03:00.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽說你有很好表現呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.45,0:03:03.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,維多利亞這裏也聽到你的傳聞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.98,0:03:05.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不喜歡傳聞的戰績
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.92,0:03:07.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我喜歡被敵人定為目標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.85,0:03:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被已方期待有實力以上的結果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.12,0:03:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳聞很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.36,0:03:16.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的傳聞如何呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.43,0:03:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,據聞你培育宇宙用的駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.50,0:03:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有很大成效
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.17,0:03:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作為戰鬥員的完成度很高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.30,0:03:24.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，諾茵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.64,0:03:26.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並非那麼喜歡戰爭的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.77,0:03:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何要這樣做?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.44,0:03:34.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你記得我討厭戰爭，我很榮幸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.08,0:03:37.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我喜歡宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.29,0:03:45.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到達地底100米
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.89,0:03:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到達無重力狀態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.33,0:03:49.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!宇宙用機動戰士操作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.49,0:03:51.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最終測試開始   知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.37,0:03:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們在做什麼!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.80,0:04:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種速度就一團糟怎辦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.04,0:04:02.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用身體感覺自己人的一舉一動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.01,0:04:04.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑克斯特尉馬上就要來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.88,0:04:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們不要出醜!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.81,0:04:08.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑克斯上級特尉他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.78,0:04:11.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道!   我們會努力   好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.72,0:04:15.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑克斯，我們已經1年22日沒見了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.84,0:04:36.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又消失了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.21,0:04:37.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.71,0:04:40.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然那是唯一\N能確認的機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.65,0:04:43.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但經過赤道後就失去蹤影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.11,0:04:45.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目標是諾茵基地的[陶拉斯]吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.62,0:04:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聯合軍太經率了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.59,0:04:48.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在維多利亞基地製造
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.95,0:04:51.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙用機動戰士陶拉斯這件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.39,0:04:53.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連平民的小孩也知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.69,0:04:56.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且，我突然前去那裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.46,0:05:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,除了諾茵之外...\N不會有人歡迎我這個掃把星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.40,0:05:03.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兩位是維多利亞\N培訓所的同學呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.70,0:05:06.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你很清楚啊   當然知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.74,0:05:08.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會不認識維多利亞畢業生裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.61,0:05:12.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,得到最高成績的頭兩名學生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.41,0:05:13.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.51,0:05:15.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑克斯特尉您一直都是第一名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.75,0:05:19.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她很倒楣，老是第二名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.72,0:05:22.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他不斷向我挑戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.35,0:05:24.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我又要麻煩她了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.37,0:05:38.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑克斯.馬吉斯…\N不，匹斯克拉福特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.50,0:05:41.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快來見我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.74,0:05:48.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今日，各位的訓練也完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.68,0:05:51.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們能忍耐我的\N無理要求，很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.38,0:05:52.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從今日起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.72,0:05:55.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位就成為SMS的一份子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.90,0:06:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這些陶拉斯會成為敵人的目標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.74,0:06:18.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以，成為OZ一份子後的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.74,0:06:20.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一個任務就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.14,0:06:22.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,立即把它們運離這基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.08,0:06:25.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那交給運輸組就行吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.49,0:06:31.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可沒教出保護不了自己機體的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.36,0:06:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說過吧，這刻不容緩...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.22,0:06:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,立即準備   知道!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.21,0:06:49.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,何時能運走陶拉斯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.14,0:06:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明早7時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.84,0:06:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很緊迫啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.38,0:06:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽說雷達對它們無反應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.41,0:06:57.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我增加了陸軍士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.48,0:07:00.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是最佳方法，不愧是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.62,0:07:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很高興得到你的讚賞，傑克斯特尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.79,0:07:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫我傑克斯，諾茵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.39,0:07:09.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，這間房很華麗啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.23,0:07:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏有很多想玩耍的年輕士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.93,0:07:14.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我認為這點設施是必需的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.90,0:07:17.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果太投入，分離會痛苦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.67,0:07:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多謝關心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.97,0:07:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我教出來的士兵絕對不會死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.34,0:07:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰術上沒有"勉強"這回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.08,0:07:30.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我認為生命的等級和生存無關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.08,0:07:32.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看過部下的死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.05,0:07:35.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,諾茵，我對你持反對的意見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.35,0:07:38.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拚命的戰鬥只是錯誤的計算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.76,0:07:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,衰老而死的戰士並不悲哀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.37,0:07:48.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是諾茵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.40,0:07:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑克斯，奧圖特士找你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.64,0:07:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏的技師也吃一驚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.11,0:07:59.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們說這部機動戰士的完成度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.38,0:08:00.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比想像中高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.71,0:08:03.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且會比預期中更快完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.38,0:08:06.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，我猜也須要一兩個月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.65,0:08:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎，我很期待，拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.22,0:08:45.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發生什麼事!?   敵襲!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.46,0:08:48.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,駕駛員訓練生的宿舍被炸毀了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.23,0:08:49.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.07,0:08:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好嚴重!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.07,0:09:01.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,教官…我想去宇宙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.84,0:09:06.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找出敵人!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.38,0:09:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一發現就攻擊把他消滅!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.81,0:09:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來會進行機動戰士戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.62,0:09:12.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,裏歐全體出動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.42,0:09:14.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人應該會立即出現!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.59,0:09:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑克斯特尉方面如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.16,0:09:21.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他說立即從南面機庫趕來這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.93,0:09:23.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.16,0:09:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信敵人是要擊毀陶拉斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.46,0:09:26.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全體各就各位!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.63,0:09:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把陶拉斯運進運輸機要30分鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.33,0:09:32.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，30分鐘後立即出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.47,0:09:34.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我負責指揮機動戰士部隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.11,0:09:36.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒敵機反應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.34,0:09:37.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,閘門沒敵機反應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.98,0:09:39.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一切正常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.65,0:09:47.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,簡直沒有敵機蹤影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.82,0:09:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,究竟躲在哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.69,0:09:57.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,映出全部基地的通路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.47,0:10:03.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.63,0:10:05.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能趕來的就來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.20,0:10:06.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾亞利茲快點出擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.67,0:10:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,追擊逃走中的敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.55,0:10:21.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停車!不停車我就攻擊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.62,0:10:24.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你逃不掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.12,0:10:26.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有援軍嗎!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.59,0:10:27.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼彈!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.33,0:10:33.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼彈可能在敵人的逃走方向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.93,0:10:35.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出動宇宙用雷射炮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.73,0:10:38.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，在地面\N使用不能完全散熱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.87,0:10:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要緊，能發射一炮就行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.21,0:10:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.08,0:10:49.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,諾茵去追敵人了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.35,0:10:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向著前方森林前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.72,0:10:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但到此為止了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.94,0:11:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然使用卑鄙戰術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.57,0:11:15.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不攻擊機動戰士而攻擊駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.97,0:11:17.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那也算是男子漢嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.81,0:11:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是個自以為是的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.32,0:11:26.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小孩!?少年?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.35,0:11:29.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是這少年\N單槍匹馬攻擊基地?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.32,0:11:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,女人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.76,0:11:34.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以很天真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.34,0:11:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想不到是單獨行動的敢死士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.57,0:11:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大約十多歲嗎? 來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.36,0:12:10.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發現目標，發射!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.03,0:12:12.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.10,0:12:14.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,諾茵特尉，為什麼!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.10,0:12:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為她是女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.07,0:12:22.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這傢伙!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.39,0:12:39.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.32,0:12:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,裝好所有陶拉斯就立即起飛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.33,0:12:44.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是諾茵特尉的命令，快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.80,0:12:47.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人不會來這裏，別慌張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.93,0:12:50.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這基地的事請你交給我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.57,0:12:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑克斯特尉，請你命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.34,0:12:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,將一號機前的專機移開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.34,0:12:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使是這基地諾茵的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.34,0:12:57.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也不會聽從
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.88,0:13:00.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別運走陶拉斯，敵人不會來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.61,0:13:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別管!\N只是二號機也好，出發!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.02,0:13:06.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑克斯特尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.18,0:13:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要接受軍事審訊啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.52,0:13:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在我比你冷靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.89,0:13:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冷靜作出判斷後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.46,0:13:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論之後有何結果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.43,0:13:17.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也不會後悔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.01,0:13:35.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快動!可惡!\N怎麼了?艾亞利茲!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.56,0:13:52.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陶拉斯…!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.21,0:14:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,女人，你聽到嗎?女人!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.38,0:14:08.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以為是小孩就大意的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.61,0:14:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是個無用士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.35,0:14:14.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不殺弱者和女人!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.46,0:14:24.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.84,0:14:42.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,絕緣部2600…還可以修理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.98,0:14:46.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，我在叫你聽見沒?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.39,0:14:51.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你為何不接受我們的好意啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.59,0:14:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難得我肯把你的機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.39,0:14:57.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和我的一起修理，你卻拒絕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.37,0:15:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很簡單，我不希望別人碰我的機體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.37,0:15:01.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是如此而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.37,0:15:02.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.57,0:15:05.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真嘴硬，你又沒有後備零件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.41,0:15:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有零件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.57,0:15:11.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,技術怎樣好的\N技師也不能修理啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.48,0:15:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,機械不像你的腳\N用力就能修理好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.11,0:15:16.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你明白嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.38,0:15:23.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,該死，我為何會救這種人出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.12,0:15:26.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愛說話、個性又不合群
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.06,0:15:28.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真受不了!如果我是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.63,0:15:31.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有那種陰沉性格，我早就死掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.93,0:15:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事呀?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.03,0:15:37.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你現在叫我幫你也太遲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.37,0:15:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你給我安靜一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.64,0:15:43.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道，對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.05,0:15:51.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.05,0:15:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是任務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.78,0:15:55.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人運來鋼彈合金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.79,0:15:58.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道，明早完成任務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.39,0:16:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以這機體的狀態你怎做得到?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.19,0:16:04.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒理由做得到吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.40,0:16:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你做不到，我做得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.57,0:16:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道，是我不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.44,0:16:15.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出錯就自爆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.94,0:16:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不容任務失敗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.04,0:16:20.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這傢伙要拚命到哪個地步?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.01,0:16:26.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.55,0:16:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你快點來殺我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.53,0:16:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根據特列斯上級特校的報告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.66,0:16:43.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那果然是由鋼彈合金製成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.70,0:16:46.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此   特列斯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.40,0:16:49.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,SMS的特列斯‧克修裏那達嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.37,0:16:50.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽聞鋼彈合金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.77,0:16:54.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只能在宇宙空間煉成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.11,0:16:55.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們果然應該斷定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.71,0:16:58.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是衛星派來的機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.12,0:16:59.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.38,0:17:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我軍解除武裝這個當前問題...不得不延後了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.55,0:17:04.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，應該反過來才對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.99,0:17:06.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也想派我國的宇宙軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.59,0:17:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去洛蘭捷點協助賽普提姆將軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.69,0:17:13.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本國也已經準備好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.66,0:17:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，把一少部分人的行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.53,0:17:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當作衛星整體的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.44,0:17:20.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,藉次迴避當前問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.17,0:17:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我認為有點不妥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.94,0:17:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是迴避問題!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.64,0:17:26.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,將軍，請立即發出攻擊命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.51,0:17:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,衛星的人比任何人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.05,0:17:31.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,更強烈希望地球圈得到和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.18,0:17:33.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們才是希望和平的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.88,0:17:35.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是，衛星的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.42,0:17:37.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嫉忌我們而有所行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.35,0:17:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.62,0:17:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當初是聯合軍單方面的武力鎮壓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.56,0:17:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,挑起了戰端...才造成這樣的結果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.56,0:17:45.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是你的本性!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.86,0:17:48.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是衛星派來的間諜吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.87,0:17:50.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在胡說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.70,0:17:53.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的報告我聽完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.07,0:17:56.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望德利安外務次官你退席
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.21,0:17:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼不清醒一點?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.74,0:18:01.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真正危險的人是你們自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.98,0:18:04.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡!你指誰!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.85,0:18:11.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在洛蘭捷點佈陣嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.19,0:18:13.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也認為那是對的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.72,0:18:16.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今次的事很有效
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.53,0:18:18.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧是傑克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.40,0:18:20.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做得很好...效率很高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.53,0:18:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,另外，蕾蒂‧安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.93,0:18:26.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,德利安外務次官方面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.10,0:18:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.11,0:18:31.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下次入浴時\N我會準備玫瑰香精
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.91,0:18:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.22,0:18:49.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知他在想什麼，晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.65,0:19:09.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.75,0:19:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難以置信!那傢伙真了不起啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.69,0:19:19.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一晚就修理好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.89,0:19:22.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被坑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.13,0:19:24.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙從這裏拆去了零件!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.33,0:19:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.83,0:19:28.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,稱讚他一下就陷害我!\N可惡!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.64,0:19:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目標確認
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.71,0:20:44.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大部份都修好了
